Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard the rumors about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Give back old diamond-head's gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean old man Cricket's stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I give anything back?\NI stole that stuff as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a pirate yourself, you're in\Nno position to find fault with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my friends. So I'm stealing it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"100 Million Man! World's Greatest\NPower and Pirate Blackbeard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask, but can you fight?!\NDo you know how to throw a punch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a coward like you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No doubt about it! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you still got that?! Tear it\Nup and throw it away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this wanted poster is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Bellamy stands a chance\Nagainst a 100 million-Berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! Just look at that runt!\NDoes he look nefarious to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me suspicious of his\N30 million bounty poster, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just stand there in\Nfear like this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you ain't gonna steal\Nnothing from me, coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That so? And just how is it different?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll shut your\Nsmart-alecky mouth for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Straw Hat flew, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateur trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd that runt come all the way here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all sit back and enjoy Bellamy's "show"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He talked all big, but now\Nhe's just running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's different at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna steal the gold back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a weakling who's all talk,\Nwho can't stand up to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and can't do anything but\Nblather on about dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's coming this way!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle all you want--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no escape from my\NSpring-Spring Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished already? Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that kid can stand\Na chance against Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't kill you, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to kick the bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My show's just getting to the good part!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did this when Roshio\Nthe Executioner was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your friends, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that geezer and\Nthose giant apes are just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a clan of natural-born\Nmorons who believe in a fish story
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,told by some guy 400 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A city of gold? A sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The era of dreams is over,\Nyou pathetic excuses for pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know how to throw a punch, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im, Bellamy! That moron\Nisn't fit to live in reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Quit kiddin' around, Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! You're just joking, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bellamy! Quit acting dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, get up! Continue\Nyour usual show! Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a major rookie with a 55 million reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Those two from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bounties are higher than yours, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-See! I told you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy's gold. Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they're tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got all beat up,\Nbut now they're just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Chopper tended to 'em,\Nbut they almost seem immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, "Don't fight! Do this! Don't go! Go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean, they beat you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't really standing\Nin our way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fights that leave nothing\Nbut sympathy are rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and get lost! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what?! You're the one who never listens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why do I have to listen to you?!\N--Hey, now! Be careful there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys insane?! This ship\Nis our treasure! Hey! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That runt... It was a fluke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I'm still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can lose\Nto dream-chasing morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Hey, Straw Hat!\NWhere're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the ones\Nwho defeated Sir Crocodile,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy... and Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scars on the back are a swordsman's shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to surpass me! Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those kids've grown to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they can shake up\Nthe World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:06.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Holy Land of Marie Jois"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Red-Hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:17.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He is acting disturbingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I assume he didn't take action himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He did so indirectly, using a messenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too dangerous for Whitebeard\Nand Red-Hair to make contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:39.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"World Government Supreme Authorities\N'The Five Elder Stars'"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Red-Hair is formidable only when agitated;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is not the type to change things\Nabout the world on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us be patient and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords of the Sea\Nare more important now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find a successor for Crocodile quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not underestimate his loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The collapse of the Three Great Powers\Nwill fracture the world itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balance must be maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! That is why we have\Ncalled the Seven Warlords here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but who knows how many will show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pirates. They do as they please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Crocodile. You've put\Nus in a dreadful situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer let this man\Nwho beat you remain unchecked...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy HQ to MaryJoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Quixote Doflamingo-sama\Nand Bartholomew Kuma-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Seven Warlords of the Sea have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Warlord of the Sea Don Quixote Doflamingo\NFormer Bounty: 340 Million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Warlord of the Sea Bartholomew Kuma\NFormer Bounty: 296 Million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My hands are moving on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! This is no time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking! I can't control my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell you can't...! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you trying to kill me?!\N--It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Where you do think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:02.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy HQ Vice-Admiral\N'Great Tactician' Tsuru"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo! This is your doing! Stop it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start talking already,\Nor I'll end this lousy get-together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You idiot! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Make him stop, Doflamingo! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fools! Did you\Ncome here to start a war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:36.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy HQ Fleet Admiral\N(Naval Commander in Chief)\N'Saint Sengoku'"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon my late welcome.\NThank you for coming, scum of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Listen to the big-shot talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us begin. I doubt any more will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two out of six is better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't plan to come either, but my\Nisland's business is going so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I came out of sheer boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's disconcerting to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is as depressing to us\Nas a booming pirate industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite in-your-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betray the "Saint" in your name,\NFleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear dreary bickering...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I perhaps come to the wrong place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy HQ and the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That roundtable seems meaningless\Nfor those two opposing powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! A most unexpected man has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm simply an onlooker here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit interested in some pirates\Ninvolved with the issue at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I, too, am an onlooker...\NIs that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I'm not exactly an "onlooker"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! How did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what a truly eminent-looking\Ngroup you have here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come in the hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--...that I be allowed to join in your meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe you have\Nstripped Crocodile of his title
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are now looking for a successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...! Are you Lafitte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lafitte?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a well-known\Npeace officer in West Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was chased from his country\Nfor being excessively violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who I am is of no importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to recommend a certain man\Nfor the Seven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks... That name brings back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a letter from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It appears to be important,\Nso he gave it to me to deliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Well done, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm still new to the Red-Haired Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Red-Haired Pirates (Newcomer)\NRockstar\NBounty: 94 Million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was a pirate before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think I made a bit of a name for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys've heard of Rockstar, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Never heard of 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, the Sea King tasted great...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending me a damn letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did that kid stoop\Nto being such a big-shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acted like this was an important letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Red-Hair you're dealing with!\NAre you sane in the head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain. That's probably\Nenough alcohol for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Something you drink when\Nyou wanna drink can't be bad for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss said this was an urgent letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea what it's about.\NAce and Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go tell that kid Red-Hair\Nthat if he wants to talk to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to come here himself,\Nand with some good booze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go! I don't feel like talkin'\Nwith snot-nosed runts, you buffoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:07.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Strongest Man in the World 'Whitebeard'\NThe Great Pirate Edward Newgate"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man hasn't changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I had an inkling this'd happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a little more time! I've never\Nbeen insulted like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! What're you\Nplanning to do? Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help.\NYou can come straight back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, I have my pride...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is more important than your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do now.\NSorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're you gonna do, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going. Prepare to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the government\Nwill keep quiet if you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government probably won't stay quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if they're gonna get in our way,\Nwe won't stay quiet, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! It's battle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Get some top-quality alcohol ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The captain of our pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of him.\NSome random, unknown guy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be no threat to other pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that end, we are carefully devising a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I ask for a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! C'mon! Let 'em try, Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Blackbeard Pirates.\NPlease remember that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?! Bellamy was beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! By who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of ambitious spirit, I didn't\Nthink he was even worth 30 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think it was this high...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the plan, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't just stand there gawking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really ticked off right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut... up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got no business with small-fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for a head\Nworth over 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to join the big leagues now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to hunt some prey has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Weren't we supposed to\Nmeet up with Lafitte in this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:59.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Helmsman\N'The Champion'\NJesus Burgess"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems we got separated!\NBut that's how luck is sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Auger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Captain\N'Blackbeard'\NMarshall D. Teach"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Sniper\N'The Supersonic'\NVan Auger"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely! Destiny always\Nmeasures a person's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:27.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Doctor\N'The Reaper'\NDoc Q"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old diamond-head! I got your gold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:22:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:23:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! I'm scared here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being sucked into the whirlpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said anything about a\Ngiant whirlpool! This is a scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's turn back! The sky island\Nis just a dream within a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island in a dream within a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll regret it for life if I pass\Nup such a big adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take to the Sky!\NRide the Knock-Up Stream"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
